[Screams]

01:27:42.674 --> 01:27:45.843
I'm the winner!
[Laughing]

01:27:45.927 --> 01:27:48.095
Now, this is
a mature relationship.

01:27:48.179 --> 01:27:52.140
% Acting erratically
Need you fanatically %

01:27:52.182 --> 01:27:57.978
% You get to me magically
sure as the sky is blue %

01:27:59.563 --> 01:28:04.025
% Baby, I love you %

